description:
Discover the charm of Yolo County’s wine country this season by visiting our Yolo Wines wineries. From cozy tasting rooms to stunning vineyard views, each tasting room offers award-winning wines, hometown hospitality, and wines perfect for gifting.  Gather your friends, sip something new, and make this season a little more delicious. 
Visit https://www.yolocountywines.com/events to see holiday winery events and to plan your wine trail! 
